Standardization Attribute Modeling: Led model maintainance and updates including evaluations and model fine-tuning. The updated model and API will be deployed in QA in June 2025, targeting over 50% adoption rate as the key OKR this year.

Data Modeling Assist: Oversaw development of the Data Modeling Assist tool. QA deployment is underway, with the MVP launch the end of June.

Research & Innovation: Directed two major researches on ontology knowledge graph and LLM expansion for abbreviations and acronyms. Our abbreviation expansion study was submitted to EMNLP 2025.

Other Collaboration: Partnered on New Metadata Guard, SCAN, Data Assist, and other organizational initiatives. Provided subject-matter expertise and hands-on support to drive collective goals.
